9GAG Test Application

The application is universal and designed both for iPad and iPhone.

The app supports infinite scrolling and loads more and more pictures when the user scrolls.
The app has 3 tabs and supports left and right swipes to change the selected tab.
The app receives JSON data from a server.

The app consists of data and UI. The key data class is DataManager. The key UI class is ViewController

Used libraries: AFNetworking, DFImageManager.
DFImageManager is need to load images asynchronously.